OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FHere, ITV News explains what your
OL,7,Frights are if your flight is delayed
OL,8,For cancelled and whether you could be
OL,9,Fdue compensation.
OL,11,FWhat are my rights if my flight is
OL,12,Fdelayed or cancelled?
OL,14,FUnder UK law, those affected by flight
OL,15,Fdelays or cancellations have legal
OL,16,Frights which oblige airlines to
OL,17,Fprovide support to customers flying
OL,18,Ffrom a UK airport, arriving in the
OL,19,Fcountry on a European Union (EU) or UK
OL,20,Fairline, or arriving at an EU airport
OL,21,Fon a UK airline.
