OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FThis usually comes in the form of
OL,7,Fvouchers, but if an airline cannot
OL,8,Fprovide food and drink or voucher
OL,9,Fequivalent for whatever reason,
OL,10,Fcustomers can make their own
OL,11,F"reasonable" arrangements and keep
OL,12,Ftheir receipts to claim the money back.
OL,14,FThis can include not just food and
OL,15,Fdrink, but also the cost of calls,
OL,16,Faccommodation and transport to a hotel
OL,17,For home. The CAA adds that "luxury
OL,18,Fhotels and alcohol" are unlikely to be
OL,19,Fcovered.
