OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my flight is
OL,4,Cdelayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FAirlines are required to pay
OL,7,Fcompensation if flights arrive more
OL,8,Fthan three hours late, but only when
OL,9,Fit is deemed to be within their
OL,10,Fcontrol.
OL,12,FFor example, a fault with the aircraft
OL,13,For pilot sickness.
OL,15,FCauses of disruption classed as
OL,16,Foutside their control include severe
OL,17,Fweather, air traffic control
OL,18,Frestrictions and security alerts.
